videos.description: Syracuse's Brittney Sykes drives through the middle of the defense and gets the and-1 layup to drop.
videos.headline: Brittney Sykes pumped up after and-1 layup

videos.description: Syracuse's Alexis Peterson gets a steal and follows it up with an assist on Brittney Sykes' layup.
videos.headline: Syracuse turns defense into offense with Sykes layup

videos.description: Notre Dame's Brianna Turner makes an and-1 shot from under the rim to give Notre Dame their first lead against Syracuse.
videos.headline: Notre Dame takes first lead off Turner and-1
